{
 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Convergence of AB4\n",
    "\n",
    "We consider the IVP $u'=\\sin[(u+t)^2]$ over $0\\le t \\le 4$, with $u(0)=-1$."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "using FundamentalsNumericalComputation"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 7,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "\u001b[36mODEProblem\u001b[0m with uType \u001b[36mFloat64\u001b[0m and tType \u001b[36mFloat64\u001b[0m. In-place: \u001b[36mfalse\u001b[0m\n",
       "timespan: (0.0, 4.0)\n",
       "u0: -1.0"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 7,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "ivp = ODEProblem((u,p,t)->sin((t+u)^2),-1.,(0.0,4.0))"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "We use a solver from `DifferentialEquations` to construct an accurate approximation to the exact solution."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 8,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "u_exact = solve(ivp,reltol=1e-14,abstol=1e-14);"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Now we perform a convergence study of the AB4 code."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 9,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "n = @. 10*2^(0:5)\n",
    "err = zeros(size(n))\n",
    "for (j,n) = enumerate(n)\n",
    "    t,u = FNC.ab4(ivp,n)\n",
    "    err[j] = maximum( @.abs(u_exact(t)-u) )\n",
    "end"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "The method should converge as $O(h^4)$, so a log-log scale is appropriate for the errors."
   ]
  },
